<div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50 py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-8 mb-6">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">キャンペーン送信前の決済確認</h1>
      
      <div class="mb-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">キャンペーン情報</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>タイトル:</strong> <%= @campaign.title %></p>
        <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>配信先数:</strong> <%= current_user.push_subscriptions.where(status: "active").count %>件</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>1配信あたり:</strong> ¥50</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-indigo-50 border border-indigo-200 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-900">合計金額</p>
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-600">¥<%= @delivery_cost.to_s.reverse.gsub(/(\d{3})(?=\d)/, '\1,').reverse %></p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">
        決済が完了すると、キャンペーンが自動的に送信されます。
      </p>

      <%= link_to "決済に進む", checkout_confirmation_path(campaign_id: @campaign.id), 
          class: "w-full bg-indigo-600 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-700 font-medium text-center block" %>
      <%= link_to "キャンセル", user_campaign_path(current_user, @campaign), 
          class: "w-full bg-gray-200 text-gray-800 py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-300 font-medium text-center block mt-4" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

